sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Process
    participant F as Filesystem
    participant S as Scheduler
    P->>F: File I/O request
    F-->>P: I/O will take N ticks
    P->>S: Block (IO_BLOCK)
    S->>S: Context switch to next process
    Note over F: N ticks later...
    F-->>P: I/O complete
    P->>S: Unblock (READY)
